---
title: Mangia Mozzarella Burgers with Pepper Relish and Roasted Garlic Aioli
description: Ketchup-slathered burgers are due to be broken out of their comfort zone, and luckily, our chefs know allllll the tricks. This recipe takes the classic dish on a trip to Italy! Melty mozzarella-topped beef patties are stuffed between toasty buns with a tangy-sweet bell pepper and onion relish and creamy roasted garlic aioli. On the side, there’s a heap of seasoned oven fries (because how could we not)?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mangia-mozzarella-burgers-b64843e7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mangia-mozzarella-burgers-5de6dbf9612733721c30a30e-de875511.pdf
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mangia-mozzarella-burgers-5de6dbf9612733721c30a30e
nutrition:
  calories: 1000 kcal
  fat: 55 g
